title: Sunshine Daydream [Untouched]
description:
Sunshine Daydream (August 27, 1972, Old Renaissance Faire Grounds, Veneta, OR)

Straight from the Blu-ray disc, I simply named the appropriate .m2ts file to reflect the title of the Blu-ray. Basically the same as the other SSDD I put up, except that for whatever reason when I converted the other to .mkv approximately 3GB was stripped away. So for those diehards that want it untouched, here ya go.
